INSERT INTO
    ip_address_bans
SET
    ip_address = ?,
    maybe_target_user_token = ?,
    mod_user_token = ?,
    mod_notes = ?
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
    expires_at = NULL,
    deleted_at = NULL,
    ip_address = ?,
    maybe_target_user_token = ?,
    mod_user_token = ?,
    mod_notes = ?
